Package: neutRal
Type: Package
Title: Spatially Explicit Neutral Community Simulations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Duccio", "Rocchini",
           email = "duciorocchini@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for simulating spatially explicit neutral community dynamics,
    visualizing species distributions, and calculating biodiversity metrics.
    The package implements grid-based neutral models with immigration,
    speciation, and local dispersal.
